CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper August 9, 1947, pg. 17, reads: "Posing Prettily - Posing for the cameraman at The Courier Chapel picnic at South Park Lodge last Friday were, left to right, front: Mrs. Marian West, Mrs. Margaret West. Back: Fred Bedell, host, and George West. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Marian West and Margaret West in front, and Fred Bedell and George West in back, seated on picnic table for Courier Chapel picnic at South Park
